Interface Emit.IListener<A0>

  • Type Parameters:
    A0 - the type of the first argument you expect to receive in handleEvent()
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCallback, AbstractCallback.Canned, AbstractCallback.NOP, EmittingCallbackFn, EmittingCallbackFn.NOP, Request
    Enclosing class:
    Emit

    public static interface Emit.IListener<A0>
    Client Interface to listen to "events". For documentation, you get to declare in what you expect the first argument to be. However, internally, there are unchecked casts so this is not assured.
